headline: Intel Bets on AI to Slash Costs
summary: Intel will reportedly outsource marketing to a consulting company that will rely on artificial intelligence.  Layoffs in the marketing department could meaningfully cut Intel's operating costs.  Other layoffs in manufacturing could help boost the gross margin, which has tumbled in recent years.
